right_now_you_support: se_ Right now you and other participants support:

participants_who_support_the_garden_get_: se_Participants who support the garden get a green leaf next to their profile picture and can add photos to rides.
how_garden_works: se_Here’s how the self-sustaining garden works.
we_share_the_costs_equally: se_We share the costs equally when we share rides together. We can do this with the costs of this app as well.
we_phrase_this_philosophy_as: se_We phrase this philosophy as “an self-sustaing garden”. We like gardens.
transparency: se_As an garant for your support of the movement being handled fair we have a non-profit assocation who is a juridicial person in Sweden.
the_key_here_is: se_The key here is that this form guarantees transparancy. But we don’t stop there, we always show you exactly where your support goes, right here in the app.

your_support_is_payed_via: se_ Your support is payed with your iTunes account or Google Play depending on your device. If you like to continue to support the movement you don’t have to do anything, your support will be auto-renewed. You can turn of auto-renewal by going to your settings in the iTunes store or Google Play.
we_will_fill_up_one_bar_at_the_time: se_ We fill up one bar at the time. The money is handled transparantly by our non-profit assocation. See more about the association and the costs under “Read more”.

if_you_decide_not_to_continue: se_ If you decide not to continue any of the support, which is sad, you can do that anytime you feel like to from the support type above.
